上游 ZooKeeper 软件开启 SASL 认证
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
上游 ZooKeeper 软件开启 SASL 认证, 需要下游 Kafka 软件服务注册时附带用户口令:

    /etc/kafka/jaas-client.conf
    -----------------------------------------------------------------
    Client {
        org.apache.kafka.common.security.plain.PlainLoginModule required
        username="kafka"
        password="kafka_4U";
    };

上游 ZooKeeper 软件开启 SASL 认证, 建议下游 Kafka 软件服务注册时启用 ACL 特性:

    /etc/kafka/server.properties
    -----------------------------------------------------------------
    zookeeper.set.acl=true

""""""""" 维护 Kafka 软件使用的主配置文件和 SASL 客户端文件
[root ~]# vim /etc/kafka/server.properties
... ...
... ...
zookeeper.set.acl=true
... ...
... ...
[root ~]# vim /etc/kafka/jaas-client.conf
Client {
    org.apache.kafka.common.security.plain.PlainLoginModule required
    username="kafka"
    password="kafka_4U";
};
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ✻

""""""""" 维护实用工具内的 SASL 配置项
[root ~]# vim /usr/local/kafka/bin/kafka-server-start.sh (45)
... ...
... ...
export JMX_PORT=9094
export KAFKA_OPTS="-Djava.security.auth.login.config=/etc/kafka/jaas-client.conf ${KAFKA_OPTS}"
exec $base_dir/kafka-run-class.sh $EXTRA_ARGS kafka.kafka "$@"
... ...
... ...
[root ~]# systemctl restart kafka-service
[root ~]# /usr/local/kafka/bin/kafka-cluster.sh cluster-id --bootstrap-server kafka-0.season.com:9092
